            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "id": 6167572,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 環宇-KY(4991)大跌7.19%，報148.5元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>環宇-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4991:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4991\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4991-TW</a>)25日11:38股價下跌11.5元，報148.5元，跌幅7.19%，成交5,701張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>環宇-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4991:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4991\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4991-TW</a>)所屬產業為半導體業，主要業務為砷化鎵/磷化銦/氮化鎵及碳化矽高階射頻及光電元件化合物晶圓代工。自有品牌光電元件產品之研究、開發、製造及銷售業務。相關智慧財產權授權。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>近5日股價上漲1.91%，櫃買市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲2.71%，股價波動與大盤表現同步。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+307 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+1,402 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：-398 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：-697 張</li> <li>融資增減：+3,547 張</li> <li>融券增減：+137 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6167572",
